snippet.title: LOVE 2: kuso - Gameplay Trailer
snippet.description:
kuso is a short platforming game with a minimalist aesthetic and a focus on fair yet challenging gameplay. 
• http://kuso.ge
• http://store.steampowered.com/app/578930/kuso/
• https://thatsmytrunks.itch.io/kuso

You are fiveEight. You have woken up to find the world has been replaced by terrible machinery powered by horrible means. You don't remember anything, but you find you have the ability to cheat death by leaving a shadow of yourself behind. Find your way through 25 dangerous landscapes to find freedom and the light at the end.
